   "num_creatives": null,
   "primary_text": "Struggling with fatigue despite taking iron supplements?   The problem might be synthetic iron your body can't properly absorb.   Chief Beef Liver Capsules contains heme iron - the most bioavailable form that may support absorption up to 5 times better than synthetic alternatives. Plus you get essential co-factors like B12, folate, and vitamin A working together as nature intended.  ✅ Grass-fed and grass-finished Australian beef liver ✅ Heme iron for superior absorption ✅ No synthetic binders or fillers ✅ Gentle on your digestive system ✅ Freeze-dried to preserve nutrients  Stop fighting your gut with synthetic iron.   Get the nutrition your ancestors thrived on - without having to eat liver.",
   "headline": "Your iron supplement not working? Try nature's original",
