   "primary_text": "The perfect meaty snacks for when you’re on the go. Our beef bars are made from 80g of organic grass-fed beef brisket and topside, slow dried to an incredibly nutrient dense 40g bar (we just remove the water weight) that’s tender, easy to eat and packed full of flavour and nutrients.   In fact, one bar has as much protein as 3 eggs\\! Free from all the nasty stuff you usually find in dried and cured meats.  💪 Organic, Grass-fed Aussie Beef 💪 Low Carb, High Protein 💪 Very Low Sugar (no added sugar) 💪 No Nasty Preservatives 💪 No MSG  Try it for yourself today.  These statements reflect the personal experiences of individuals and are not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. Always consult with a healthcare professional before starting any new supplement.",
