  {
   "id": "chief-aus-2-eggs-for-breakfast-2-minute-breakfast",
   "uploaded": false,
   "concept": "2 eggs for breakfast - 2 minute breakfast",
   "objective": "",
   "type": "",
   "num_creatives": null,
   "primary_text": "A breakfast that actually keeps you full. Ready in 2 minutes.  Most people skip breakfast or settle for low-protein options because they think they don't have time.   But hitting 30g of protein doesn't need to be complicated.  Greek yoghurt (10g protein) + Chief Whey Protein (22g protein) + nuts + berries = 30g of protein that keeps you full, sharp, and energised until lunch.  Perfect for busy mornings when you need real nutrition fast.  💪 30g Protein In 2 Minutes 💪 Keeps You Full Until Lunch 💪 22g Grass-Fed Whey Per Serve 💪 Zero Bloat  Stop skipping breakfast because you're \"too busy.\" This takes less time than making toast.  Subscribe and save 10% plus free shipping.",
   "headline": "A Breakfast Ready In Minutes",
   "cta": "",
   "landing_url": "https://wearechief.com/products/grass-fed-whey-protein-powder-smooth-chocolate-30-serves",
   "campaign": null,
   "adset_hint": null,
