  },
  {
   "id": "chief-aus-2-eggs-for-breakfast-30g-protein-changes-everything",
   "uploaded": false,
   "concept": "2 eggs for breakfast - 30g protein changes everything",
   "objective": "",
   "type": "",
   "num_creatives": null,
   "primary_text": "Less than 30g of protein at breakfast sets you up to fail the entire day.  Without enough protein, you're hungry by 10am, your blood sugar is all over the place, you get brain fog by lunch, and your body starts breaking down muscle for energy.  But when you hit 30g at breakfast, everything shifts: stable energy, clear thinking, no cravings, and you actually stay full until your next meal.  Chief Whey Protein makes hitting 30g easy. One serve gives you 22g of clean, grass-fed Australian whey protein that won't wreck your gut like other powders.  💪 22g Grass-Fed Whey Per Serve 💪 Stable Energy All Day 💪 No Bloating 💪 Easy to Digest  Stop surviving on low protein and start actually thriving.  Subscribe and save 10% plus free shipping.",
   "headline": "Why 30g Of Protein At Breakfast Matters 💪",
   "cta": "",
   "landing_url": "https://wearechief.com/products/grass-fed-whey-protein-powder-smooth-chocolate-30-serves",
   "campaign": null,
   "adset_hint": null,
   "creatives_folder": "https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1M8zzeH4ELvzs5ITAaGvHg9AjiEyu6IS8?usp=drive_link"
  },
  {
   "id": "chief-aus-2-eggs-for-breakfast-2pm-slump-started-at-breakfast",
   "uploaded": false,
   "concept": "2 eggs for breakfast - 2pm slump started at breakfast",
   "objective": "",
   "type": "",
   "num_creatives": null,
   "primary_text": "That 2pm energy crash? It didn't start at 2pm. It started at breakfast.  When you don't get enough protein in the morning, your blood sugar spikes and crashes throughout the day.   You're on an energy rollercoaster - hungry every few hours, reaching for snacks, feeling foggy, and barely making it to the afternoon.  The fix is simple: hit your protein early with Chief.  One serve in your morning coffee, yoghurt, or smoothie gives you 22g of grass-fed whey protein.   💪 22g Grass-Fed Whey Protein 💪 Stable Energy All Day 💪 Real Food, Zero Bloat 💪 Mix Into Anything  Stop blaming coffee for your energy problems. Start with protein.  Subscribe and save 10% plus free shipping.",
   "headline": "Your 2PM Crash Started At Breakfast",
   "cta": "",
   "landing_url": "https://wearechief.com/products/grass-fed-whey-protein-powder-smooth-chocolate-30-serves",
   "campaign": null,
   "adset_hint": null,
   "creatives_folder": "https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1LnpQfquwZYDodaD4qqXRaqGxkFQXZrwL?usp=drive_link"
  },
  {
   "id": "chief-aus-2-eggs-for-breakfast-the-energy-timeline",
   "uploaded": false,
   "concept": "2 eggs for breakfast - The Energy Timeline",
   "objective": "",
   "type": "",
   "num_creatives": null,
   "primary_text": "The difference between a low-protein breakfast and a high-protein breakfast isn't subtle.  Low protein (less than 20g): You're hungry again an hour later. Your energy is all over the place. Brain fog hits by lunch. You're fighting cravings all day.  High protein (30g): You stay full for hours. Stable energy that lasts. Clear thinking. No mid-morning snack attacks.  Chief Whey Protein makes hitting 30g simple.   Add one serve (22g) to your regular breakfast—whether it's yoghurt, oats, or even your coffee—and you're set.  Made from 100% Australian grass-fed whey. No fillers, no sweeteners, no bloating.  💪 22g Grass-Fed Whey Per Serve 💪 No Fillers or Sweeteners 💪 Easy to Digest  Stop starting your day at a disadvantage.  Subscribe and save 10% plus free shipping.",
   "headline": "Starving By 10AM? Here's Why...",
   "cta": "",
   "landing_url": "https://wearechief.com/products/grass-fed-whey-protein-powder-smooth-chocolate-30-serves",
   "campaign": null,
   "adset_hint": null,
   "creatives_folder": "https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1_BdHMg0tCCT_bL6QusnFKB55RxMRVT_f?usp=drive_link"
  },
  {
   "id": "chief-aus-2-eggs-for-breakfast-protein-shakes-for-gym-bros",
   "uploaded": false,
   "concept": "2 eggs for breakfast - Protein Shakes for Gym Bros",
   "objective": "",
   "type": "",
   "num_creatives": null,
   "primary_text": "Think protein shakes are just for gym bros trying to bulk up?   That's the myth keeping most people from hitting their daily protein needs.  Protein isn't about muscles. It's about how you function every single day.  30g of protein per meal helps you think clearer, stay full longer, keep your blood sugar stable, and actually have energy past 2pm. It supports your immune system, helps you recover faster, and stops the constant snacking cycle.  Chief Whey Protein delivers 22g of clean, grass-fed Australian whey per serve. No artificial sweeteners, no fillers, no gut-wrecking junk. Just real food protein your body needs—whether you lift weights or not.  💪 22g Grass-Fed Whey Per Serve 💪 No Artificial Sweeteners or Fillers 💪 Easy to Digest  Everyone needs protein. Not just gym bros.  Subscribe and save 10% plus free shipping.",
   "headline": "Protein Isn't Just For Gym Bros 💪",
   "cta": "",
