   "id": "chief-usa-beef-liver-menopause",
   "uploaded": false,
   "concept": "Beef Liver Menopause",
   "objective": "",
   "type": "",
   "num_creatives": null,
   "primary_text": "Beef liver is one of the most nutrient-dense foods on earth—but most modern Aussies haven't eaten it in years.  What makes it unique? Naturally occurring heme iron—absorbed at rates up to 35% compared to plant-based iron's 2-20%. Your body recognises heme iron as food, not a synthetic compound.  Chief Beef Liver provides traditional whole food nutrition without the taste or prep:  ✅ Naturally occurring heme iron (from grass-fed beef)  ✅ Pre-formed Vitamin A + complete B-vitamin complex ✅ Zinc, copper, and folate  ✅ Organic Australian cattle  ✅ Freeze-dried to preserve nutrients  ✅ No hormones, antibiotics, or synthetic fillers  Real food nutrition in capsule form.",
   "headline": "Why Nutritionists Call Beef Liver \"Nature's Multivitamin\"",
   "cta": "",
