   "type": "",
   "num_creatives": null,
   "primary_text": "\"We've finally done it: Chief's Grass-Fed Whey Protein is here - and it's everything you'd expect from us.  Most protein powders are loaded with cheap fillers, artificial sweeteners, and processed ingredients that do more harm than good.  Chief's Creamy Vanilla Grass-Fed Whey Protein keeps it simple: premium whey protein concentrate from 100% Australian grass-fed dairy cows, minimally processed to preserve nutrients and natural taste.  💪 100% Grass-Fed Australian Whey 💪 No Sweeteners, Fillers, or Sugar Alcohols 💪 Tested Free From Hormones & Antibiotics 💪 Naturally Occurring BCAAs 💪 Mixes Smoothly, Tastes Great  Whether you're building muscle, managing weight, or recovering faster - this delivers without the junk.  Mix with water, blend into smoothies, or add to oats - boost your protein with something your body can actually use.  Real ingredients. Real results.\"        Introducing Grass-Fed Whey Protein 💪",
