   "primary_text": "Introducing the ultimate protein boost for your busy life: Chief's Collagen Protein Powder, exclusively sourced from premium 100% Australian grass-fed bovine.  Just like our beef bars, but this time, we've taken the best parts of bovine collagen, hydrolysed it into super absorbable peptides, and packed it into a powder that's as easy to use as it is beneficial for your body.   Each serving helps support your muscles, joints, skin, and gut with less effort and more impact. Which means you get all the goodness of collagen, the body’s building block, without any fuss.   💪 100% Aussie Grass-fed Bovine Collagen 💪 Highly Bioavailable for Rapid Absorption 💪 Bloat-Free Goodness 💪 Absolutely Zero Sugar 💪 Free from the Nasties: No artificial additives or preservatives  Our Collagen Protein Powder is great for when you’re on-the-go and you need that extra protein punch.  Add it to your morning smoothie, coffee, tea or even your pancake batter to start your day with a boost that’s both delicious and nutritious.",
