   "primary_text": "Most supplements weren't made for this stage of life. \nThey were made for women in general which means they're missing exactly what your body needs right now.\nPerimenopause changes your hormones, your metabolism, your sleep, your mood. A one-size-fits-all formula from the chemist shelf wasn't designed for that.\n\nHormone Balance Plus was.\nFormulated specifically for women 35–55. Symptom-specific ingredients. Australian-made, triple lab tested, TGA listed. No fillers. No guesswork.\n\nAnd if you don't feel the difference in 60 days? Full refund. No questions asked.\nYour body deserves better than generic. 💙",
